       <strong>Phone:</strong> (555) 123-4567<br>
       <strong>Hours:</strong> Mon-Fri 9am-6pm, Sat 10am-4pm</p>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
.faq-widget { max-width: 600px; margin: 20px 0; }
.accordion-item {
  border: 1px solid #ddd;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  border-radius: 4px;
}
.accordion-header {
  padding: 15px;
  background: #f5f5f5;
  cursor: pointer;
  margin: 0;
  font-size: 1em;
}
.accordion-header:hover {
